Watching this intro guide:

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=i04Rgnn2XbI&ab_channel=ParwizForogh

1. We create a free postgresql database on api.elephantsql.com (can be done other places)
2. We download pgAdmin and enter the information of the database

go to servers-->[name of db]-->databases--> find the relevant one (yellow color) --> schemas --> public


